nodes.text: Oosea was a male Ithorian from the planet Ithor. Unknown to the rest of his herd, he began cooperating with the Galactic Empire. With his cooperation, the Imperials began plans to create a base on the planet Ithor. When Oosea was discovered, he framed his fellow Ithorian Ire Eleazari. Eleazari was banished from the herd after being framed, but worked with the Erling Tredway to clear his name.
